gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 109, Heat 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nets defeated the Heat, 109-105. Mikal Bridges recorded 21 points, seven rebounds and five assists for the Nets, while Armoni Brooks added 17 points and two rebounds in the victory. Tyler Herro tallied a game-high 30 points, along with five assists for the Heat in the losing effort. The Nets improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Heat fall to 1-4.
